org.concordion.cubano.data

Class EntityPool<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.concordion.cubano.data.EntityPool<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - Class of the entity being held
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataCleanup

    public abstract class EntityPool<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataCleanup

    Maintains a global pool of of available entities and those that are in use.

    request() and release() methods: It is expected that the implementing class implement methods that call these - allows for customisation.
